---
title: Thai-Spiced Pork and Cilantro Rice with Dressed Veggies
description: Pork chops marinated in ginger and Thai-style spices get thinly sliced and served atop a bowl full of fluffy basmati rice for tonight's delicious dinner! We've added marinated cucumbers and shredded carrots, and herby cilantro for extra flavour and freshness.
